Lingua/TH/Segmentation version 0.01
=====================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

(should compile from the source)

glib-2.0
Libthai (http://linux.thai.net/libthai)
TH word segmentation library (http://thaiwordseg.sourceforge.net)

